==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/ l /, often transliterated as l. Pronounced alone it is / lə / similar to the beginning of the English word [[love]].

===Letter===
'''ल''' (l)
#The third [[semivowel]] of the [[Devanagari]] script, but traditionally classified (and [[collated]]) as a consonant. Linguistically it is considered a lateral dental/alveolar [[approximant]].

